tk biding events
| event                 | name                  |
| Ctrl-c                | Control-c             |
| Ctrl-/                | Control-slash         |
| Ctrl-\                | Control-backslash     |
| Ctrl+(Mouse Button-1) | Control-1             |
| Ctrl-1                | Control-Key-1         |
| Enter key             | Return                |
|                       | Button-1              |
|                       | ButtonRelease-1       |
|                       | Home                  |
|                       | Up, Down, Left, Right |
|                       | Configure             |
| window exposed        | Expose                |
| mouse enters widget   | Enter                 |
| mouse leaves widget   | Leave                 |
|                       | Key                   |
|                       | Tab                   |
|                       | space                 |
|                       | BackSpace             |
|                       | KeyRelease-BackSpace  |
| any key release       | KeyRelease            |
| escape                | Escape                |
|                       | F1                    |
|                       | Alt-h                 |
